  "title": "FACILITIES MANAGEMENT EXECUTIVE",
  "description": "<h5>Job Description &amp; Requirements</h5>\n<p><strong>Job Descriptions</strong></p>\n<p>1) Keep facilities and common areas clean and maintained.</p>\n<p>2) Vacuum, sweep, and mop floors.</p>\n<p>3) Clean and stock restrooms.</p>\n<p>4) Clean up spills with appropriate equipment.</p>\n<p>5) Notify managers of necessary repairs.</p>\n<p>6) Collect and dispose of trash.</p>\n<p>7) Assist guests when necessary.</p>\n<p>8) Keep the linen room stocked.</p>\n<p>9) Properly clean upholstered furniture.</p>\n<p>10) Able to work long hours, weekends, and public holidays</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p>Minimum 1 year of working experience in housekeeping and facilities management areas</p>\n<p>Minimum Diploma Holder, with a positive attitude to managing the assignment</p>\n<p>Physically fit and able to take physical requirements on the daily operational activities.</p>\n<p>Training would be provided with an assessment</p>",
